Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很襯你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我換一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點  時間有限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這邊啊  你有認真看過地圖嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到那邊的店去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把錢包給我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱著那個走？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  我知道有家很好的店…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那邊坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會賠償你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.26,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  這是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣  請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是週末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翹課了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是創校紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為出席學校的活動也很無聊  就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此  我也翹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上還黏著冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真粗心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃列斯真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商城的構造清楚了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在主街道上的防盜攝影鏡頭的數目是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,68  雖然也有一些死角  但並不適合在任務中用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別稀里糊塗地和別人扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去研究一下任務吧  行李也差不多該送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的演技…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很差呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到Zwei之後  Phantom執行任務變得更有效率了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是理想的組合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然看上去只是呆呆的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5個月不到就能進入東海岸還真值得稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮之至
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這不是很危險嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣連續出動Phantom…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如您所說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候慎重地觀察情況才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:07:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬  如果你信任我和Phantom  就請允許我們的行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保證萬無一失  我將親自到現場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  鬥志很旺盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給你的Phantom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賜予我的虛假名字  沃列斯·楊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛杉磯在讀的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與最初殺死的那男人同名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從殺了那個男人之後  我就一直在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與她一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦·路西奧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達拉斯黑手黨的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時不會從他戒備森嚴的大宅裡出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而例外會在三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了購買給孫女的生日禮物  他將會到那個商場  那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是送來的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標將會在明天下午三點左右到達現場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我們要先部署在最佳的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為最佳的位置是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是…測驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master這麼對我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混在購物的客人之中接近目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我們這樣的話  是不會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不能在商場內進行襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方太寬廣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且當天也會有許多護衛  他們還有監視攝影鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在護衛少而且不引人矚目的地方下手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在目標和護衛放鬆警惕的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答案正確
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認目標  但是我被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩人正在跟蹤我  來幫我蒙過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電梯前的噴水池  快來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我等了多久了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我都自己逛完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽你的解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想怎麼賠償我浪費的這一天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不給我個滿意的回復我就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  今天買的東西都算我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐也算？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店我已經都找好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省了不少功夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪沃列斯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標在南棟的古董商店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接他的車會轉到南出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續進行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這件比較適合您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來攻擊  拜託你掩護了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標的護衛鬆懈的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  閉幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你們兩人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讓您專程來迎接  光榮之至
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:17:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為上司  慰勞部下是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得不錯  我很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔待不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全變了個人啊  那個少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您滿意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備讓他們處理裝備之後  乘旅客機回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友等累了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是昨天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是到這裡來旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正準備回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  玩得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  希望還能再相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演技不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻在狗屋裡默默等著任務的獵犬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現在的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master說的是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他用三個月就趕超了花了兩年時間的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是過去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像看著赤裸裸的我一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回預告  剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蔽感情  扣下扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪取他人的幸福
